Class BotCliHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.view.cli.CliInputHandler
      • it.polimi.se2019.view.cli.BotCliHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    public class BotCliHandler
extends CliInputHandler
    Handles the creation of a fake player that choose randomly between the options that the server propose him. It supports random exits, choosing more items in a list, connecting with both RMI and SOCKET.
